Text:
Interesting little clip...

Can't say that listening this dubbed in German was a positive or not...Since, German is a rather a harsh to the ear type of language, I'm not sure that listening in a language that sounds more like coins dropping on the floor is a turn on either.

For what the clip is, I liked it.  She gets turned on like a light bulb getting a scrubdown, and if the guy likes eating shaving cream while having KimChee with his meal, more power to him I say!

I like this...not over done like the American 'pronos" flick (who cant act to save thier careers) this was simple and nice.

If you like a touch amature realism, then this will make it into your library...
